{"tid":1213662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致去完祈禱嘅你","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T02:19:56.000Z","uid":62252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6689e82e4c624803462ced6c3feb988fe9d16d59","tid":1213662,"uid":62252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1ZEwsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1ZEwsx.jpg&h=ffa4c996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢出咗去祈禱會又覺得好想記錄低嘅你<br />\n<br />\nsend下第一手資料比外國朋友睇下<br />\n<br />\n我哋有幾神心<br />\n<br />\n小薯冇咩做到<br />\n<br />\n本身只係諗住送下咸水去<br />\n<br />\n但都食咗幾粒<br />\n<br />\n隻眼痛到今日都係咁出眼水<br />\n<br />\n仍然想喺屋企繼續祈禱<br />\n<br />\n唔想放棄<br />\n<br />\n想見到神蹟<br />\n<br />\n做應該做嘅事"}]}